productDesc: 3-in-1 with TENS, EMS and Massage functions. Targets 3-body zones (Neck, Back and Knee) with adjustable intensity and 68 programs. Compatible with electrode pads and electrode belt, battery operated.
productDetailedDesc:
-3-in-1: TENS, EMS and Massage
-3-Body Zones (Neck, Back and Knee)
-Quick start keys (direct-buttons) for all three body zones
-2 channels with adjustable intensity
-White display backlighting
-68 programs - 30x TENS, 10x EMS and 10x Massage, 18 Quick start key programs (3 programs each body zone under TENS mode and EMS mode)
-Timer function
-Button lock function
-Compatible with electrode pads and electrode belt (Neck, Back, Knee/Elbow)
-Large, comfortable, easy approach & humanized button design
-Load detection and lock function (Doctor function) for safety use
-Battery operated
productDeliveryReturnsDesc:
Delivery

Currently delivering to selected postcodes in NSW, VIC & QLD. Your order will be dispatched within 1-2 business days and you will receive order updates via email with tracking details.


Returns

While we hope you'll be happy with your order, you can return a product to your nearest store or contact us via email to arrange. To check if you are eligible for a refund please refer to our Returns Policy.
